                        <ln>Lesher</ln>
                        <fn>Christian D.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Rowe</ln>
                        <fn>John</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Maj.</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Sellers</ln>
                        <fn>W.W.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Recommends Lesher and Wishart over Rowe and Sellers for reasons of
                    character as well as party.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <pageNote>Many articles denouncing Nill and the Republican ticket, warning voters to
                avoid the so-called Union Ticket.</pageNote>
